      "content": "that's a good start. can you make it a bit more descriptive? like, instead of just saying \"primitive,\" maybe have him describe the people or their customs in a way that really emphasizes how \"uncivilized\" or \"savage\" they seem compared to Europeans. make it sound like he's genuinely looking down on their way of life as something that needs to be corrected.",
